Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:26.10,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Drawn by a landscape as white as snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:32.65,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}I'm headed toward an unseen world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:41.58,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I've been traveling while lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.37,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Under this gray sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:50.46,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Every day with new maps, stained with my many dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.84,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I wonder if someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.88,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Even with these tiny steps of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.97,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I'll be able to travel beyond those clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.60,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I put on a bold front.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.14,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}End up hurting myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:09.23,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I feel empty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.77,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's started to rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.94,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And the raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.15,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Began to repeat their scattered reflections.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.03,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}These straight rays of light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.74,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Start to cross one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.33,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}And without telling anyone where they're headed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.62,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Across the endless distances,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.21,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They pass through all matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:34.04,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I burn these faint afterimages onto my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.96,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Under this sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.76,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}Wherever I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.09,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I should be able to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.89,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}The unseen world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:26.10,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)}{\blur3}真っ白な景色にいま誘われて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:32.65,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}僕は行くよ　まだ見ぬ世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:41.58,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}迷子のまま旅していた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.37,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}鼠色の空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:50.46,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}日替わりの地図 いくつもの夢が滲んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.84,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}いつかはさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.88,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}ちっぽけな僕のこの歩幅でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.97,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}あの雲の向こうまで行けるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.60,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.14,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}キズついた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:09.23,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}心透かしたように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.77,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}降り出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.94,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雨粒たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.15,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}乱反射繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.03,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}真っ直ぐな光が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.74,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}交差して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.33,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}行き先も告げぬまま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.62,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.21,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}突き抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:34.04,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}淡い残像　両目に焼きつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.96,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}この空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.76,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}どんなとこにいても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.09,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}届くはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.89,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}まだ見ぬ世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:26.10,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Masshiro na keshiki ni ima sasowarete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:32.65,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Boku wa yuku yo mada minu sekai e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:41.58,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Maigo no mama tabi shiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.37,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Nezumiiro no sora no shita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:50.46,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Higawari no chizu ikutsumo no yume ga nijindeita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.84,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Itsuka wa sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.88,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Chippoke na boku no kono hohaba demo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.97,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Ano kumo no mukou made yukeru kana
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.60,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tsuyogatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.14,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kizutsuita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:09.23,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Kokoro sukashita youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.77,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Furidashita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.94,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Amatsubu tachi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.15,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Ranhansha kurikaesu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.03,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Massugu na hikari ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.74,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kousa shite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.33,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Yakusaki mo tsugenumama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.62,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Doko made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.21,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tsukinukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:34.04,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Awai zanzou ryoume ni yakitsukete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.96,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kono sora no shita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.76,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}Donna toko ni itemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.09,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Todoku hazu nanda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.89,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}Mada minu sekai e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:33.41,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,657)}{\fad(500,0)}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:37.50,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to act tough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:44.30,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scribbling someone made...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:50.09,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,On the wall, of a flower is swaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:55.68,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows their true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:57.98,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we both lose and gain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:01.40,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,By embarking on this long, long path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:09.07,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}And though there may be days loneliness strikes and makes us weep...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:16.58,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's transform our tears and pains to stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:22.58,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's light a candle to illuminate our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:27.71,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll hold our small hands over the fire to create stardust,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:32.93,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And an eternity that shines so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:38.31,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewells may be unavoidable,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:44.23,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Yet the seasons continue to change obliviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:48.32,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose myself, I'll continue to walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:52.36,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:56.62,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}That's the only thing I'd like to never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:37.50,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,強がらなくていいんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:44.30,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが描いてった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:50.09,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,壁の落書きの花が　揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:55.68,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,自分らしさなんて, 誰もわからないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:57.98,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,長い長い道の途中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:01.40,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,失くしたり, 拾ったり,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:09.07,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}急に寂しくなって, 泣いちゃう日もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:16.58,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}涙も　痛みも　星に変えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:22.58,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}明日を照らす　灯りをともそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:27.71,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さな手かざして　ふたりで作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:32.93,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,星屑を　強く光る永遠を探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:38.31,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,さよなら　いつかは来るかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:44.23,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}季節はそれでも巡り巡ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:48.32,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さく迷っても　歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:52.36,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,君と歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:56.62,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}それだけは変わらないでいようね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:37.50,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaranakute iindane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:44.30,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka ga kaitetta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:50.09,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabe no rakugaki no hana ga yureru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:55.68,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibunrashisa nante dermo wakaranaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:57.98,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai nagai michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:01.40,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakushitari hirottari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:09.07,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kyuu ni samishikunatte naichau hi mo arukedo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:16.58,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Namida mo itami mo hoshi ni kaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:22.58,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ashita wo terasu akari wo tomosou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:27.71,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisana te kazashite futari de tsukurou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:32.93,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshikuzu wo tsuyoku hikaru eien wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:38.31,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayonara itsuka wa kurukamoshirenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:44.23,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kisetsu wa soredemo meguri megutteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:48.32,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisaku mayottemo aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:52.36,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi to aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:56.62,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}Sore dake wa kawaranaideiyoune
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:02.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You believed the enemy's words and lost the will to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.48,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose your composure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.65,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Do not simply accept death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:15.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you are truly my aide, then keep your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:17.99,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:23.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to continue to rely on you to watch my back. Be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.58,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to talk, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:29.17,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of commander wanders out in a mission like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:29.88,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-ow-ow-ow-ow-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:36.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why am I in the same room as you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't hospital rooms supposed to be singles with beautiful nurses?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:40.89,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:43.98,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's much easier for me to guard you two if you're recovering in the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:45.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's worrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't they come to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.69,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let the flame guy leave alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.82,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He burned Lust to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.70,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Lust... died...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late! Go kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.00,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Roy Mustang. We can use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.67,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Use? Don't tell me you're going to make him open the...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.42,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:17.26,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Father put me in charge of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What if it's decomposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.19,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:58.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,My body on the other side of the gate hasn't taken in any nutrition!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I was able to return to a body like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Winry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.25,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Ed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:16.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is only hypothetical, but when we tried to transmute Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:20.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,we used our blood in the formula as information for her soul, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:21.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:26.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we were both taken to\Nthe other side and were decomposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:34.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a possibility our minds were entangled during that process?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:41.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wondering if it's possible your body and I are connected in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You know, for my age, I'm sh-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:48.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Short...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.33,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,He said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He was able to face reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.71,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying your growth is connected to how Al would have grown?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.51,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds crazy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's not crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.55,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You're short because you never drink milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.43,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, Brother is always sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be he's making up for my sleep, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.15,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I said, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.40,Default-alt,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.82,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.83,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Paying the Colonel a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Havoc is injured, too,\Nso we wanted to pay them a proper visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:37.13,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I would be here today\Nif the Colonel hadn't come to our rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you're here, too, Sergeant Fuery?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.88,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Running some errands for the Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:49.60,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I've calculated the approximate distance to that large door...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.27,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,...by counting the steps I took since entering Research Laboratory 3's basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:59.56,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The exact direction is unclear, so I drew a circle with the laboratory at the center, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Central headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, this building is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The Homunculi reside under there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:16.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a chance the Führer President has connections to them... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:22.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If he does, then I wonder why he killed Greed and his crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's still suspicious, even if he doesn't have ties to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He killed them all without even trying to extract information from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.06,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President... He's mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, the enemy has infiltrated pretty high up in the military command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We ought to approach him with caution from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.11,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal. Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.82,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculus and the Führer President...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.87,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to fish out something larger than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.91,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I also have a feeling it's a bit too large...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be worthwhile otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a lot of work for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.55,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.97,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.43,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... feel my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.14,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.65,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like an early retirement for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.78,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.82,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.24,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Backache.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.33,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Coroners are always standing,\Nso it's a tough job for old guys like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:44.25,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I knew right away when I heard you were the one who killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.25,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:50.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So you declared that thing was Second Lieutenant Ross when you knew I was up to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,War buddies are wonderful to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:56.97,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,We're not war buddies; more like accomplices in crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:00.35,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You burned them up; I dissected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.48,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbal was a giant experimental site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.70,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep taking risks like that, you'll get tit for tat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.50,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,My comrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.84,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...is paralyzed from the waist down due to a spinal injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:37.97,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,And I just got permission to have one smoke a day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:43.90,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, isn't that just hilarious?\NGetting stabbed by a woman and having to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.98,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do after you retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.28,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,My family runs a general store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.90,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I can at least help out by answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.66,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get an automail?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:02.50,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's not possible since the neural network for the entire lower half of my body is disconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.84,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Retirement doesn't suit you one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:12.97,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.09,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,About Havoc's legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.81,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,...here's some information I got from the Fullmetal boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,An alchemist well-versed in medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.73,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Philosopher's Stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.40,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible to have my vacation extended?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:31.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I permit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.20,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.62,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.25,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Are you back from your vacation, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.54,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,How was your trip to the east?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.04,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.30,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It was a nice place with lots of beauties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.51,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.13,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.30,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,This is from military police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.72,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,They want all the State Alchemists to know first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:04.85,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They let me in without objection when I told them I was a State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What about the entrance to the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But there were traces of it being covered up with alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're not so stupid as to leaving the entrance wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:33.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not possible for us to go\Nand meet the Homunculi from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:39.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They said something about not wanting me killed because I'm an important sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They said that to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That I could become a sacrifice because I'd opened the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is that these sacrifices...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:50.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...are alchemists who are capable of opening the gate and returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:54.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are they planning on doing by making us sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat it out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.03,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Edward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sergeant Brosh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.74,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.00,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to go back to the hotel immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.42,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish, I'll call for escorts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.84,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,A notification to the entire city from military police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.76,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Scar has appeared in Central once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.68,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Three casualties, all of whom are State Alchemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.51,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Several others wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:25.77,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,According to witnesses, he has a large cross-shaped scar on his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:29.98,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,An Ishbalan with tattoos all over his right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Tattoos... on his right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Scar killed the Rockbells?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's not certain yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you can't tell Winry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to see her cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to face Scar again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to try to find out the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That, too, but I have something else in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use him to lure out the Homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They want to keep me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So if I'm attacked by Scar and in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They'll show themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's very likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But it's better than sitting around and doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:32.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But we were defeated by him in an instant last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:37.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we've... gotten a bit stronger-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And even if the Homunculi do show themselves, how do we catch them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are they strong,\Nbut they're pretty much invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.81,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Invincible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.26,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.10,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Immortality, correct?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,From the window again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.27,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lend you a hand with that mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.07,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,We're not interested in all the military troubles,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.66,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,but if it's about Homunculi or immortality, we can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.45,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you doubting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful you rescued Second Lieutenant Ross, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.08,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,The more people by your side, the better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.63,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,We're serious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.38,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of an entire clan rests on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not run off with the Homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:36.40,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep our promise! We owe you for a meal, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Room service?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.74,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,This place has great food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"A meal" my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.20,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.33,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get up early tomorrow,\Nbut I can't sleep with all this noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:56.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. So you're going back to Rush Valley tomo-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:03.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, cancel the trip and stay in Central for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:03.92,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know. How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My arm may break again, or more accurately... it's definitely going to break again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.73,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning to break it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Brother's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.44,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.36,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything too dangerous, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.16,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.54,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.72,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Nice try, nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,A deadlock, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.49,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,My mother and someone from the Department of Veteran Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.71,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I've completed the retirement procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.88,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been determined if you'll be able to recover, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.63,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so stupid as to not understand I'm useless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.42,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.01,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a chess piece that can't move, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.52,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea how pathetic of a look you have right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.98,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me behind! Throw me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.61,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have time to be worrying about an underling like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.48,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a promise to keep with Brigadier General Hughes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.32,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.32,Default-alt,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Havoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.16,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.16,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you behind, so you'd better catch up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:21.98,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:32.49,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even abandon me;\Nsomeone who tried to accept death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.53,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he'd rely on me to watch his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.45,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,He can't throw his men away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.33,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,He's an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:46.34,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can reach the top of this country with a soft attitude like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:51.22,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better for everyone\Nif an idiot like that exists among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Bring my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.73,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no condition to be discharged from the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.03,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.66,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:22.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have to close down for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you guys are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:30.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,State Alchemist, Edward Elric, to the rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.51,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much! How much should I pay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely no need for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:48.23,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I broke a precious jar. Could I ask you to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:07.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Edward Elric, your city's State Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.54,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Please fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:16.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The whole city is talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,With that flashiness, it's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have expected things like this from you, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're well enough to leave the hospital already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about Second Lieutenant Havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask Dr. Marcoh, he can probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hold that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.78,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We're in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh is missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably abducted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.13,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard about Scar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing things that will just catch his eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I need to fight him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.98,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what happened to you in East City?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:12.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Afraid of Scar now, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:17.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty much useless\Nlast time, if I remember correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me! The weather's fine today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, you're exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You really are useless, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Now look! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:34.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? It's not even raining, but you look pretty drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:37.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.05,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:43.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd try fishing like the Colonel likes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:52.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to drag out the Homunculi, using Brother as bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:56.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Since Brother is an important sacrifice and they want him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want any more casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:03.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So either me or Brother have to be the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:09.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What if Scar gets shot to death by the\Nmilitary police before the Homunculi come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.42,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You can take care of that, right, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Ordering me about now, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you do capture the Homunculi, give me a crack at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.09,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Fuery's second home is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.35,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.23,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You two! Please back away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot! You'll hit Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... if Scar gets shot, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Not being too close or too far is a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to get here, Homunculus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.96,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The channel for the military police headquarters is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less to be expected from Fuery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,3rd District Military police unit reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently fighting Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.73,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Requesting reinforcements immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.48,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You! What... are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the 17th district next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.86,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:19.48,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.44,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:23.20,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Scar is in the 17th district, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.86,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was with the 3rd district?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Douglas! He's shown himself in 8th district, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:28.41,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.87,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Central military police headquarters, reporting to the 8th district.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Scar and a boy are engaged in combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The boy is a State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Do not shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There are false reports all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A fourth Scar?! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.30,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 3rd district! Everything is in order!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.59,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 8th district! We've found Scar! Requesting reinforcements immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.43,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.60,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell it. I can smell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.61,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of that Ishbalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.03,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I sense something... Did you, Ran Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.86,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.11,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:09.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Which is he after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Human destruction or my automail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.58,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I got lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:25.26,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He canceled out the decomposition energy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.84,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Tattoos on his right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.19,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell it. I can smell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.40,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.61,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,You have a strange interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.12,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,How many people do you have inside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.41,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.70,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in trying to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:58.08,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense your distinct aura from a mile away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:00.96,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy? Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.26,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Can I eat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.34,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.09,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,A Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:10.59,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You can sense us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:15.56,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,A troublesome ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.69,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eliminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:20.69,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Ran Fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:22.23,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.24,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Ran Fan!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:03.21,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,The shriek of the hurt girl echoes throughout Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.87,0:24:08.05,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,When the trampling force meets his past again,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:10.38,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,memories of violence are awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:16.22,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:19.97,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 22, Backs in the Distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:22.14,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to protect her."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.48,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,That was the thought in the boy's mind.
